			<div class="content">I run an SSD. Got a small SSD (actually 60G which is not really small) and a really cheap external disc USB cabinet (smallish box). The cabinet came with a power cable, USB in one side. I found a USB charger 2amps with two outlets. One outlet goes to the pi and one goes to the SSD. Short USB cable from pi to SSD.<br /><br />It works quite well.<br /><br />Links to what I got:<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.webhallen.com/se-sv/hardvara/139495-ocz_intern_ssd_60gb_vertex_plus_series_sata_ii_2.5">http://www.webhallen.com/se-sv/hardvara ... ata_ii_2.5</a><!-- m --><br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.webhallen.com/se-sv/hardvara/114486-deltaco_externt_kabinett_2.5_sata_till_usb_2.0-aluminium-plast_svart-silver-glansig_ytfinish">http://www.webhallen.com/se-sv/hardvara ... g_ytfinish</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Cannot find link to the USB Duo charger.<br />//Gunnar</div>

			

