			<div class="author">by <strong><a href="./memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=18233&amp;sid=469102a612be38316c03a171bfcf5c2f">Alfadaz</a></strong> &raquo; Tue Nov 06, 2012 5:17 am </div>

			

			<div class="content">As above really, i have the rev 1 board and couldn't run much from the USB port.  <br /><br />Since I have bypassed the polys (and done the wire on the back hack) I can almost run a 2.5&quot; SATA drive from it.  I say almost because i can connect it and it mounts and can get small files, but when running Raspbmc and trying to stream i get lock ups, which i presume is lack of power.<br /><br />Daz</div>

			

